      <item>Tasks 024-028 use the new `ExecutorType` name in updated dispatch logic.</item>
      <item>Sibling worktrees may need to rebase after this PR merges; coordination per task 021 plan.</item>
    </related-work>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Rigor Declaration">
      Output: 🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL · 📋 REASON: code-impl in BFF; refactor tag; ADR-010+013+029+038 applicable; large diff (~1000+ references); quality gates Step 9.5 required · Proceeding with Step 0...
