      Rename the enum declaration `ActionType` → `ExecutorType`. Apply Roslyn-aware refactor (IDE Rename Symbol) so all references update including XML doc `&lt;see cref=...&gt;` references.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Sweep edge cases">
      Per audit 020 list: review string literals (`"ActionType"`), JSON property name attributes, log message text, and any remaining edge cases not handled by the Roslyn rename. Update each manually.
    </step>
